data.description: Welcome to this meticulously updated end-unit townhome in the heart of Acton Village! Boasting over 1600 sq ft of thoughtfully designed living space, this residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. Step inside to discover the warmth of wood-look LPV flooring that guides you through a spacious layout. The inviting living room, complete with a charming brick fireplace, sets the tone for cozy evenings. Entertain guests in the formal dining room, where a sliding glass door seamlessly connects indoor and outdoor living.The kitchen is a chef's delight with stainless steel appliances, modernized cabinets, and a convenient pass-through to the living room, ensuring you never miss a moment with family and friends. Upstairs, the owner's suite is a sanctuary with a dramatic vaulted ceiling and a well-appointed en-suite bath. Two additional guest bedrooms, a remodeled hall bath, and a convenient upper-level laundry area complete the second floor.This home is not only stylish but also energy-efficient. A brand new HVAC system ensures year-round comfort, while a one-year-old solar panel system not only aligns with eco-conscious living but also generates surplus power, earning you credits each month. Step outside to the fenced backyard, where a brick paver patio invites relaxation, and two sheds offer ample storage. The architectural shingles on the roof are in great condition. Good condition, a desirable location, and a GREAT price.  Simply a must see.
